headline: BTQ Technologies Corp. Execution of Definitive Agreements for C$40 Million Previously Announced Offering
summary: BTQ Technologies Corp. (the "Company") (CBOE CA: BTQ) (FSE: NG3) (OTCQX: BTQQF), a global quantum technology company focused on securing mission-critical networks, is pleased to announce that its previously disclosed C$40 million financing (the "Offering") is fully subscribed, with definitive agreements executed by all participating investors.
